We provide three input files:
(1) input_use_node_init.inp: We use different number of neurons for different models.
(2) input_use_seed_init.inp: We use different initial values in different models.
(3) input_mtd.inp: We use metadynamics trajectory in lammps for model deviation.
We runing deepff calculation, please be careful to set environment. We recommend add
these lines in submition script:
export OMP_NUM_THREADS=1
export PATH=deepmd-kit_path/bin:$PATH
If you want to use GPU in deepmd-kit, please add these lines in submition script:
module load cuda/10.0 (We use module to add environment of cuda. For your systems, 
                       please change it if you do not module tool.)
export KMP_BLOCKTIME=0
export KMP_AFFINITY=granularity=fine,verbose,compact,1,0
